HTML-FormHandler-View-Email version 0.01
========================================

Module to easily and dynamically generate Emails from HTML::FormHandler classes.

Type the following after installing for more information:
     
     perldoc HTML::FormHandler::View::Email

INSTALLATION

To install this module type the following:

   perl Makefile.PL
   make
   make test
   make install

DEPENDENCIES

This module requires these other modules and libraries:

Moose
Email::Sender::Simple
Email::Simple::Creator
Email::Sender::Transport::SMTP
Email::Simple
HTML::FormHandler::Moose;
HTML::FormHandler

